data.description: Nestled on .40 acres of picturesque countryside, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a dream for those yearning to experience the tranquility of country living without sacrificing proximity to the city. Priced to sell, this property offers an extraordinary opportunity for those willing to infuse some Tender Loving Care (TLC) into its character. The abundance of natural light streaming through the home highlights its potential, and with a 2-car attached garage, convenience blends seamlessly with rural charm. Imagine relaxing on your porch, taking in the scenic views behind your new home. What makes this opportunity even more enticing is the option to assume the current FHA loan, providing a pathway to homeownership that is both accessible and advantageous. Don't miss the chance to make this house your dream country home – an oasis that awaits your personal touch and vision.
